docs.abstract: At least six women have accused University of Wisconsin senior Alec Cook of sexual assault; revelations have shaken campus while also revealing continued reticence of some women to file complaints of sexual assault, even as campuses across nation openly confront problem; prosecutors have formally charged Cook, calling him serial sexual predator who targeted fellow college students on Madison campus.
